{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The repository already has durable revisions for some artifacts, but I need to see whether selection/current-pointer semantics and restore/compare are missing or inconsistent across outline, pitch, character, and beat flows. I\u2019m narrowin...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_4", "text": "The repository already has durable revisions for some artifacts, but I need to see whether selection/current-pointer semantics and restore/compare are missing or inconsistent across outline, pitch, character, and beat flows. I\u2019m narrowing onto the session service, hydration schemas, database models, and the workspace stage components now.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 11, "prompt_index": 57, "prompt_name": "56 \u2014 Revision History and Branch-Like Tracking for Plan Changes", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T04:14:42-07:00"}
