{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The composition service currently captures beat-sheet and setup IDs, and outline details only inside job metadata. That\u2019s workable but not explicit enough for reviewer-grade plan lineage, so I\u2019m checking the frontend contracts to add a s...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_22", "text": "The composition service currently captures beat-sheet and setup IDs, and outline details only inside job metadata. That\u2019s workable but not explicit enough for reviewer-grade plan lineage, so I\u2019m checking the frontend contracts to add a single understandable revision summary instead of leaking raw backend internals into the UI.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 44, "prompt_index": 57, "prompt_name": "56 \u2014 Revision History and Branch-Like Tracking for Plan Changes", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T04:15:29-07:00"}
