{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented prompt 56 end to end and checkpointed it at commit `753f7a2` on the current branch. The change adds durable `plan_revisions`, explicit composition-to-plan lineage, a restore endpoint, non-destructive planning revision behavio...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_303", "text": "Implemented prompt 56 end to end and checkpointed it at commit `753f7a2` on the current branch. The change adds durable `plan_revisions`, explicit composition-to-plan lineage, a restore endpoint, non-destructive planning revision behavior, and a new `PlanRevisionHistoryPanel` wired into the pitch, character, beat, and story-setup stages. The required reviewer summary was written last to [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/56_revision_history_and_branch_like_tracking_for_plan_changes/summary.md).\n\nVerification completed with targeted backend suites (`83` relevant tests passed across session/story-tools/api/hydration/migration coverage), frontend unit tests (`43` passed), frontend lint/build (passed; build emitted the existing chunk-size warning), focused Ruff checks on all task-touched Python files (passed), and live browser QA against the Docker Compose stack. Browser verification confirmed the restore UI changed the current saved plan from `Otter Bell Moonpath` to `Lantern Harbor Promise`, with screenshots at `.artifacts/webapp-qa/revision-history-before.png` and `.artifacts/webapp-qa/revision-history-after.png`. Repo-wide backend format/lint still has pre-existing unrelated baseline issues in untouched files; that is documented in the summary.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 588, "prompt_index": 57, "prompt_name": "56 \u2014 Revision History and Branch-Like Tracking for Plan Changes", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T04:55:19-07:00"}
